<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_386" id="192r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_386_r1l8"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ludweıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>pfallncʒgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> bey Reyn <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l9">in Peyern vnd Grafen cʒu Graıſpach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_386_r1l10"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als vns <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat / wıe dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l11">werde gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> neẅ ſtraſʒen ſuchen vnd faren etc das haben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l12">wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l13">hannſen Erlpeken <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> . dem wır befolhen <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l14"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dauon ʒu reden . Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſʒ . was </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l15"><expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu dıſem male von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅr gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l16">werbe . / Daʒ Jr Jn darinn <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> verhören . Jm des gencʒlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l17"><expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd auch <expan>günſtıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> fertıgen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l18">wellet / als etc Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> / dıenſt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_line_1577281212669_4666">wolgefallen etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_386" id="192r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ludweig<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        bey Reyn, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan> in Peyern und grafen czu
                        Graispach</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von Werde gen
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> new straszen suchen und faren etc.,
                        das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> Hannsen Erlpeken,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> davon zu reden; und
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
                        mit fleisz, was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> zu disem male von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr gnade werbe, daz ir in darinn
                                <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> verhören, im des genczlich
                                <expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch
                                <expan>günstikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> fertigen wellet. Als etc. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
